title: This is just too easy! Home in Graham. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: Welcome home to this move in ready, fully fenced, 3 bedroom home situated on just under a half acre.
Spacious island kitchen with granite counter tops open to nice sized family room is great for entertaining.
Primary bedroom w/ 5 piece bath and walk in closet.
Additional secondary bedroom has its own walk in closet.
Simple, manageable landscaping w/sprinkler system water feature and inviting extended covered back patio.
